php-mpdf (8.3.2.4) stable; urgency=medium

  * fix(autoload): use php-setasign-fpdi system package instead of bundled
    vendor/setasign/fpdi — load setasign\Fpdi\ via its own autoloader at
    /usr/share/php/setasign/Fpdi/autoload.php; version bumped above 8.3.2.3
    so that upgrades from older builds succeed (8.3.2+deb1 sorted lower)
  * docs: document fpdi dependency and correct usage example in README.Debian

 -- Vítězslav Dvořák <info@vitexsoftware.cz>  Sat, 18 Apr 2026 23:55:00 +0200

